Package ui.scene

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CampaignCreationScene
    This class is used to layout the campaign creation scene.
    CampaignEditingScene
    This class is a subclass of Scene and implements the interface MapDelegate.
    EditorScene
    This class for choosing editor and creation.
    FinishScene
    This class is the last scene in whole game, and it can back to MainScene with ending the campaign.
    ItemCreationScene
    This is a ItemCreationScene to show the scene for creating item name which extends Scene class
    ItemEditingScene  
    MainScene
    This is the Main Scene class extends Scene class
    MapCreationScene
    This is a MapCreationScene to show the scene for creating map name which extends Scene class
    MapEditingScene
    This MapEditingScene class is for editing game map view which extends Scene class And implements GameMapView.Delegate, PlayerDelegate, EquipmentDelegate
    PlayCreationScene
    This class extends Scene and implements PlayerDelegate and CampaignDelegate.
    PlayerCreationScene
    This is a PlayerCreationScene to show the scene for creating onPlayer name which extends Scene class
    PlayerEditingScene
    This is a class for players to create or edit the details of their characters.
    PlayScene
    This is a PlayScene for onPlayer to play on created maps.
    ReadyScene
    This ReadyScene means players have already created a play within onPlayer and campaign.
    Scene
    This class is a superclass for other scenes class.
